Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.63,0:00:06.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind. Open your mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.51,0:00:22.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Far beyond the deep blue Earth,\nyou and I shall meet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.72,0:00:24.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as a gentle breeze goes by.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:28.09,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.09,0:00:29.56,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.56,0:00:36.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A snow-white feather will come\nfluttering down, swaying gently in the air.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:43.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without holding back, I want to\nenvelope you, my one and only love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.81,0:00:53.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know I have the power to protect\nthe one I love, right here in my hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.22,0:00:59.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind.\NJust as I've always dreamed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.96,0:01:06.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let the wind carry off\nyour hopes, faraway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.86,0:01:13.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have wings nobody can see.\NLook, you have them, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.64,0:01:21.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They'll take us to where we can be free.\NAnyone can be free.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.94,0:01:26.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sky is so blue...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:38.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.56,0:01:40.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.13,0:01:43.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And she moves in such\nmysterious ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.03,0:01:46.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The more I find out about her,\nthe more she enchants me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.97,0:01:51.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.44,0:01:55.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to steal you away from\nthat guy if it's the last thing I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.44,0:01:58.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Or my name isn't Toshiyuki Aoshima!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:01.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oooh! Aaaa! Mr. Aoshima!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.25,0:02:07.51,AMG episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah! Can the Auto Club Triumph?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:11.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}RECRUITING NEW MEMBERS{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:16.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:18.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please? Just check us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:20.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.44,0:02:25.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Auto Club is currently\nseeking new members!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:27.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, anybody!\N{\i1}Please stop by!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:33.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not a soul has stopped by yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:35.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.29,0:02:43.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come hither, youths!\NCome to the Auto Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:48.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find the answers to all your\ndreams! Come to the Auto Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:50.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, freshman!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:55.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you join the Club now, I'll personally\nhonor you with my special dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:56.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.77,0:02:58.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:03:02.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We stayed up all night practicing\nour special welcome dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:04.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Den-chan, dance for him! Dance for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:06.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.48,0:03:10.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come hither, youths!\NCome to the Auto Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:13.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find the answers to\nall your dreams and hopes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:16.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's pretty lonely\nover here, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:18.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did you sign up any new members?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:20.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, not even one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:23.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder, with seniors like those...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:26.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why don't you join?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:29.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I've already\njoined the softball team!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:31.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.24,0:03:34.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's just been too\nfew people stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:40.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Usually we get a few students who are\ninto cars coming over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:42.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's that over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:45.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's the Auto Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:48.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you might as well skip them\nand join the Four Wheels Club instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:50.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They've got a lot of girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.53,0:03:56.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Four Wheels Club?\nI've never heard of that club.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:04:00.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I saw some\nskanky people making a lot of noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:03.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was somewhere over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.08,0:04:10.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The NIT Four Wheels Club is\ncurrently seeking new members!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:13.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Join now, and you'll\nreceive a free invitation to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:17.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...our Welcome Party,\naccompanied by all these ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:20.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Count me in!\N{\i1}Me, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:22.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Since when do we have a club like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:25.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to give a\nlittle extra effort, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:27.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Den-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:29.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with you, Dai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.57,0:04:32.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're just gonna drive away\neven more people...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:37.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then! I'll just give them\na boost with my sexual charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:41.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what we need, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But we have an Auto Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:46.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they doing this?\nIt's like a personal attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:50.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In order to get rid of\nthe Auto Club, that's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:51.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aoshima!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:55.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A dingy club like yours is an\nembarrassment to our institution.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:58.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've established the\NFour Wheels Club with...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:05:00.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the intention of having\nthe Auto Club shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:03.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who you callin' dingy, hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:05.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We clean out our club room!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:08.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, at least once a year...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:11.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think the Auto Club\nis a wonderful club!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:15.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:18.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'd like to propose a challenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:19.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:23.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whichever club loses the next\nIntercollegiate Rally agrees to break up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:26.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How does that sound to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:28.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We accept your challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:31.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:34.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you quite sure? If you lose,\nyour club will have to disband.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:35.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um, that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:40.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right... may the best team win!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:42.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:44.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:46.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:49.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry. We won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:55.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She is absolutely right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:06:00.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Our Auto Club cannot suffer defeat\nat the hands of those newcomers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:02.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:04.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But how can we race with no machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:06.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't have one, we'll build one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.56,0:06:08.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have the parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.23,0:06:09.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll buy them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:11.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But we have no money...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:14.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've got the 500-yen savings\nfund we started last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:17.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That disappeared somewhere,\ncookie jar and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:23.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Morisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:24.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:26.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Willpower!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:33.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}UNDER CONSTRUCTION{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:39.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll show them what\nthe Auto Club's made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:42.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I should've seen this coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:45.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just do our best, Keiichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:49.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kiddo, it must be great to be young!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:53.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Betcha you don't get much sleep at\nnight if you're with a girl like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:53.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:57.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But why wouldn't he get\nmuch sleep if he's with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:07:00.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:09.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Heave-ho! Heave-ho! Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:12.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Heave-ho! Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:37.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:40.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, everyone\nstart looking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:42.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:45.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. You were a huge help to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:49.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If we can find the parts we need,\neverything will work out okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:50.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:54.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. At the very least,\nI think we can enter the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:55.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:56.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:08:00.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We had to rely on your help after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:03.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:07.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You came this far because everyone\nin the Auto Club worked so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:08.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.99,0:08:11.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eureka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:13.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:14.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:18.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:19.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:22.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What made you take on the challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:26.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at it,\nthe odds are against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:32.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. The odds\nmay indeed be against us...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.65,0:08:41.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But you and Mr. Tamiya and\nthe others have such love for...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:44.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...the Auto Club, such reverence\nfor the old and used, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:47.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...you've come this far\nwithout giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:52.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see how people like you could\never lose. That's what I'd like to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:54.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:04.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now, I can feel romance in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.51,0:09:05.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:09.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi, this is when you put\nyour arms around her shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.85,0:09:10.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:12.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, don't be so bashful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:13.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:16.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Like this... see? It's not hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:25.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is it, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:36.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:40.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.04,0:09:43.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, show yourself! I'll trash YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:48.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Belldandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:52.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of the Shards of Glass,\nreveal the identity of those...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:54.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...who skulk in the shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:04.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How obvious is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:08.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well! Whoever did\nthis showed no mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.53,0:10:09.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aoshima!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:11.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.74,0:10:15.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was told that the Auto Club's\nmachine had been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:18.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But, leaving it unguarded here\nwas practically...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:21.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...an invitation for someone to trash it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:23.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:28.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Was it you who smashed up this car,\nbuilt with all our blood, sweat and tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:32.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, do you have a shred of\nevidence that I committed this act?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:38.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by the extent of the damage,\nyou have no hope of repairing it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:44.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose there's no way out of it.\NShall we forget about the challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:46.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really mean that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.21,0:10:49.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... but not without\nany strings attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:54.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Morisato, you will apologize\nto me right now, in front of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:58.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do that, and we can just\nforget about the challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:05.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know all I need to know\nabout your personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:09.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're a coward who'd never rise to\na challenge if it seemed too foolhardy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:12.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If your true colors are\nexposed in front of Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:14.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...she'll be sure to dump you in disgust!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:17.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't miss with this scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:19.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's it going to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:24.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a far better option than suffering\npublic humiliation in the race, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:26.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Morisato...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:29.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:32.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:35.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be defeated\nby the likes of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:37.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, Morisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:39.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn right! You got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:42.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll let you off if\nyou apologize to us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.27,0:11:44.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your bravado will prove worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.57,0:11:45.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keiichi...{\i0}\NYour bravado will prove worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:48.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard you try,\nthere's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:50.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:54.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We will win this\ncontest, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:56.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kindly leave us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:02.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:06.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You were actually pretty cool just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:08.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:11.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But losing's not an option\nanymore, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.49,0:12:14.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because that guy really\nmade Belldandy angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:17.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Angry? Belldandy's angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.04,0:12:22.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't look mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.37,0:12:23.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:25.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:26.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:29.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:30.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I made lunch for all of you today, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.78,0:12:32.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Belldandy, about the race...{\i0}\nI made lunch for all of you today, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:33.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Belldandy, about the race...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:34.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We shall win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:36.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But with no car...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:37.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We shall win!{\i0}\NBut with no car...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:38.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And no time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:39.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We shall win!{\i0}\NAnd no time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:41.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We shall win no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:44.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You agree with me, don't you, Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:47.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:53.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now you know what the consequences\nwill be if you lose, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:55.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:19.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Go get 'em! I'll be cheering you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.43,0:13:22.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Show them how tough you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:23.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi! Win this thing, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:25.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on, Kei!{\i0}\NKeiichi! Win this thing, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.60,0:13:28.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How's it looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:30.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what do you want me to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:32.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:36.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Our adjustments are still incomplete.\NWe shouldn't be racing this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:38.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:42.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The NIT Auto Club Off-Road Special\nis in perfect condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:46.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We attached a front wheel system,\nmaking this a Three-Wheel-Drive rig!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:50.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It has vented disc brakes as well as\nan independent rear suspension...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:52.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...with gas-charged shocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:56.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We constructed the body\nfrom lightweight FRP.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:14:00.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention this high-end\nsteering column and car stereo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:04.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Plus this trendy vanity mirror\nattached to the sun visor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:08.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With all this, what else in\nblue blazes could you ask for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:11.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But this course is riddled\nwith extreme ups and downs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.18,0:14:13.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And there are even sand dunes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:16.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It would be suicidal to try and race\nin an incomplete three-wheel rig like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:19.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No way is it incomplete!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:21.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.02,0:14:23.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to compensate\nwith my driving...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.73,0:14:25.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But, Morisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:27.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it as far as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:32.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We stayed up all night fixing this\nmachine. Our love will make it run.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:34.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's the spirit, Morisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:37.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you doing?{\i0}\NThat's the spirit, Morisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:40.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's send you off with\nour cheerleader dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:47.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So they managed to fix it in time, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:48.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:52.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not to worry.\nI've planned for this contingency.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:56.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Island here.\NPut Plan A into action!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:58.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:03.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:08.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is now five minutes before the race.\NAll teams, start your engines!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:11.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I'm running late,\nI'd better hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:14.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:17.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anyone there who can help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:23.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck is she? If she doesn't\nshow up before the race begins...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:23.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...we'll be disqualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:25.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next, No. !{\i0}\N...we'll be disqualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.39,0:15:28.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Nekomi Institute of\NTechnology Four Wheels Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:35.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:40.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've hired a professional\noff-road racer for this race.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:44.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you guys will be\ndisqualified before the race starts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:45.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next, No. 16!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:46.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't see Belldandy!{\i0}\NNext, No. 16!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:48.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}NIT Auto Club!{\i0}\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:48.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}NIT Auto Club!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:49.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}NIT Auto Club!\NNo way...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:51.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's up to something again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:55.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, No. 16, NIT Auto Club?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:15:57.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be disqualified!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:15:59.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:04.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:06.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:09.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No. 16, are you dropping out\nof this race?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.93,0:16:12.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, we're on our way now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:18.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! How could she\nhave escaped from that trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:23.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I've been saying all along!\NShe's a world-class escape artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:26.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who does she think she's dealing with?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:29.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty more traps\nwhere that came from!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:38.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Decrease average to 40 and go 50R to\nthe left and go to 70 once you're past it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:41.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I would, but I can't tell\nhow fast I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:43.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:46.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the...\nthe steering wheel's suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:49.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This voice... it's the car's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:53.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your front wheel's about to go?\NAll right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:01.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:10.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What next, Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:13.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right, you need to go right 100R.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:16.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Announcing checkpoint times\nfor Checkpoint No. 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:21.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Currently leading the pack is No. 4,\nthe NIT Four Wheels Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.10,0:17:24.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:28.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In 2nd place, currently 10 minutes\nbehind, is the NIT Auto Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:30.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Despite having the smallest vehicle...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:33.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...thanks to their great chemistry,\nthey've managed to stay in 2nd place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:37.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn those pesky bastards!\NWith that patched-up machine of theirs?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:41.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's up to no good again, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:44.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better keep my eyes open!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:54.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be here any second now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:17:56.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure they don't see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.04,0:17:57.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:04.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's the steering wheel this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.41,0:18:07.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:14.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've used too much power.\NBut we don't have much farther to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:17.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy, what's coming up next?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:19.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:20.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.24,0:18:32.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:34.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy? Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:36.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:39.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:42.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You really are high-maintenance,\nyou know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:45.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're in big trouble!\NBelldandy's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:46.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.99,0:18:49.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's fallen into her dormant state,\nthat's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:50.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:54.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she used up a lot of power.\NShe's not waking up any time soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:56.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Power?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:58.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This clunker was on its last legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:19:03.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So she's been using her power\nto keep it from breaking down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:06.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what was going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:15.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame, but at this point, I guess\nyou have no choice but to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:22.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But you and the others have\nsuch love for the Auto Club...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:27.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...such respect for the old and used, and\nyou've come this far without giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:34.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see how people like you could\never lose. That's what I'd like to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:38.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So what are you going to do, Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:40.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No! I won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:44.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because I know Belldandy\nbelieves in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:46.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Attaboy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:48.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.39,0:19:53.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.66,0:19:56.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Morisato, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:59.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Morisato here. Is that you, senior?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:01.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at Point B8 right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:03.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right, gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:05.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Morisato, turn right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.07,0:20:07.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You must bear to your right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.04,0:20:08.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:11.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now passing the 3rd\nand final checkpoint...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:14.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The NIT Four Wheels Club\nremains in the lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:18.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The course is now buried\nin sand due to strong winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.91,0:20:23.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The vehicle in 2nd place is trailing over\N30 minutes behind. Hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:25.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This information just in...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:29.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Another machine can be seen\nhurtling over the sand dunes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:33.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now! It's the NIT Auto Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:35.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the... that's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:36.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:38.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Morisato!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:47.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But why would there be\na road like this here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:50.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a road...\nit's a protective bulkhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.55,0:20:51.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bulkhead?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:56.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There are bulkheads buried along\nthe coastline in this sand dune.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:57.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:21:01.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Only a three-wheeler can navigate\nsuch a narrow path!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:04.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The race is yours to win now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:05.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.56,0:21:09.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.90,0:21:13.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.44,0:21:15.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They've crossed the finish line!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:17.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,1st Place, NIT Auto Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:19.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dai-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:20.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Den-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:23.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kei, you were awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:27.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.41,0:21:28.84,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:33.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When are you gonna learn?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:35.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi would never lose to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:41.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, time for me\nto punish you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.26,0:21:45.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.57,0:21:52.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi, how did the race go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:54.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We won!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.11,0:21:57.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We owe it all to you,\NBelldandy, for believing in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.11,0:22:00.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, you won because\neveryone played a part in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.52,0:22:02.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess it's thanks to everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.62,0:22:05.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:07.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.69,0:22:13.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, such a romantic atmosphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.03,0:22:15.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, this is when you\nput your face next to hers and...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.96,0:22:16.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:17.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't be so shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.43,0:22:19.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stop it!{\i0}\NCome on, don't be so shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.43,0:22:20.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.57,0:22:23.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Would it kill you to cling to each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.38,0:22:38.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One day when I woke up...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.79,0:22:49.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A day like any other...\nanother one just beginning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.49,0:22:58.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There you are, yawning...\nyour face is still so sleepy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.97,0:23:05.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because each peaceful day\nwe share is a miracle to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.65,0:23:12.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is where my heart\nwill always return...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.25,0:23:15.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forever...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.11,0:23:21.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's only one thing I wish for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.03,0:23:27.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I chase after the same dream,\nwherever it may go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.47,0:23:33.47,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The love I feel for\nyou gives me strength.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:39.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}May tomorrow be as joyful as today...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.71,0:23:44.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's my wish...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:23:59.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A demon has been summoned\nfrom the Dark Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.27,0:24:03.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's out for revenge on the goddesses,\nchanging the human into a strange form.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.27,0:24:06.37,AMG next episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Ah! The Demon\NArrives and Wreaks Havoc?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.37,0:24:10.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Don't tell me I'm gonna\nbe like this forever?
